@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ · White Stitches";
    ViewData["MetaDescription"] = "Frequently asked questions — orders, shipping, returns, sizing.";
}

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero__inner">
    <span class="eyebrow">@L["Help · FAQ"]</span>
    <h1 class="page-hero__title">@L["Frequently asked."]</h1>
    <p class="page-hero__lede">@L["Quick answers to the questions we get most. Can't find what you're looking for? WhatsApp us."]</p>
    <p class="page-hero__meta">@L["Last updated · 10 May 2026"]</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="policy">
  <div class="policy__inner">
    <aside class="policy__toc" aria-label="@L["On this page"]">
      <span class="eyebrow">@L["On this page"]</span>
      <ol class="policy__toc-list">
    <li><a href="#orders">@L["Orders & payment"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#shipping">@L["Shipping & delivery"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#returns">@L["Returns & exchanges"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#product">@L["Product & sizing"]</a></li>
    <li><a href="#account">@L["My account & privacy"]</a></li>
      </ol>
    </aside>

    <main class="policy__main">
      <section class="policy-section" id="orders">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Orders & payment"]</h2>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["How long does it take to process my order?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Standard orders are processed and dispatched within 24 hours during business hours (Sat–Thu). Express and same-day orders placed before 2 PM are dispatched the same day.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["What payment methods do you accept?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>KNET, all major credit and debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, AmEx), Apple Pay, Google Pay, mada, BenefitPay, and buy-now-pay-later via Tabby and Tamara. Cash on delivery is also available in Kuwait for a 1.500 KWD fee.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["Can I change or cancel my order after placing it?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>You have a 1-hour grace window after placing your order to make changes via the Manage Order link in your confirmation email. After that, the order is locked for production and we can&rsquo;t guarantee changes.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["Do you offer gift wrapping?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Yes — every order can be gift-wrapped in our signature tissue with the wax-marked closure for 3.500 KWD. You can add a personal note up to 250 characters.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="shipping">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Shipping & delivery"]</h2>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["Where do you ship?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>We currently deliver across Kuwait, Saudi Arabia, UAE, Bahrain, Qatar and Oman. Other GCC and international destinations are coming in 2026.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["How long does delivery take?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Standard 2–3 working days within Kuwait, free over 50 KWD. Express next-day available for 3.500 KWD. Same-day in Kuwait City for orders placed before 12 PM. Other GCC destinations 3–5 working days.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["Will I get tracking?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Yes — once dispatched, you&rsquo;ll receive a tracking link via WhatsApp and email. You can also track from your account dashboard.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["Do you ship to PO boxes?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>No — couriers in the GCC require a physical address.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="returns">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Returns & exchanges"]</h2>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["What's your returns policy?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>You have 14 days from the day you receive your order to return any unworn item with original tags. Refunds land in 3–5 working days to your original payment method.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["Are sale items returnable?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Yes, for store credit only. Final-sale items, swimwear and earrings cannot be returned.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["How do I start a return?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Go to Account → Returns and select the order you want to return. We&rsquo;ll review and email you a prepaid label within 24 hours.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["Do you cover return shipping?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Yes for items that are defective or wrong. For change-of-mind returns, a 2.000 KWD flat fee is deducted from your refund.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="product">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["Product & sizing"]</h2>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["How do your sizes run?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Our pieces are drafted in Kuwait and run close to GCC body shapes. See our full <a href="/size-guide" class="link-inline">size guide</a> for measurements. If you&rsquo;re between sizes, we recommend sizing up.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["Are pieces restocked?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Some are, some aren&rsquo;t. We produce in small batches and decide season by season what to reorder. If a piece is sold out, add it to your wishlist and we&rsquo;ll notify you if it returns.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["How do I care for my pieces?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Care instructions are on each product page and on the garment label. Most of our pieces are dry-clean only — please don&rsquo;t machine-wash silk.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="account">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">@L["My account & privacy"]</h2>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["Do I need an account to order?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>No — guest checkout is supported. But an account lets you track orders, save addresses and access the wishlist.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["How do you use my data?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>We use your information only to process your orders and (if you opt in) to send styling notes. See our <a href="/privacy" class="link-inline">Privacy Policy</a>. We never sell your data.</p></div>
        </div>
<div class="faq-item">
          <button type="button" class="faq-item__q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>@L["Can I delete my account?"]</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-item__a"><p>Yes — Account → Profile → Privacy &amp; data → Delete account. Orders are kept for legal compliance.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</section>

